{"tid":411923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"載撕中大民主牆單張女離去　私家車主與中大榮譽教授同名","createTime":"2017-09-24T08:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T09:26:38.000Z","uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d35e5f207e58f5f8dbe08251232242252d16e1a5","tid":411923,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:24:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">載撕中大民主牆單張女離去　私家車主與中大榮譽教授同名</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170924/s00001/fc297888e30327169b5d70d24d877be8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170924%2Fs00001%2Ffc297888e30327169b5d70d24d877be8.jpg&h=811dfb0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文大學民主牆上早前出現「拒絕沉淪，唯有獨立」標語單張，上周日（17日）一名女士突然大幅度撕走標語，其後乘坐私家車離開，私家車後來駛回現場，司機開窗並大叫「英國走狗」。運輸署資料顯示，私家車車主與中大信息工程學系榮譽教授李碩彥同名。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》已電郵李碩彥查詢，暫未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n根據中大網頁，李碩彥於1970年畢業於國立台灣大學數學系，並於1974年在美國加州大學柏克萊分校取得數學博士學位。現時他同為中國電子科技大學、哈爾濱工程大學及台灣國立清華大學等學校的榮譽教授。<br />\n<br />\n事發上周日下午，一名白衣女士突然大幅度撕走中大民主牆上的港獨標語單張，正在當值的學生會外務秘書李文耀即上前阻止並詢問身分，該女士未有回應，其後乘坐私人座駕離開。約2分鐘後，其座駕駛回現場，司機開窗並大叫「英國走狗」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170924/s00001/1506238891287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170924%2Fs00001%2F1506238891287&d=gvPQCd7LuzKh4Sy6KYKq1aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f85b7980\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170924%2Fs00001%2F1506238891287&h=dac8f5e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170924/s00001/1506238891287</a>"},{"pid":"87e4593ec1f861ec791be2a8bcbe1b69136f7602","tid":411923,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd61e31bd09fd5ad583e7fbc929f9b1cc5117102","tid":411923,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}